There is an option to parse all content from o'reily API's and make .epub or .pdf file
https://learning.oreilly.com/api/v2/epubs/urn:orm:book:9781835468609/files

Integers in URL is id of book, you could find it in o'reily book page.
Use subscribed (or trial) account's cookies for successfull parsing, otherwise you will receive partial content.
